    • Method Detail

      • forElement

        XMLObfuscator.AttributeConfigurer forElement(String element,
                                             Obfuscator obfuscator)
        Sets the obfuscator to use for occurrences of the attribute for a specific element.

        This method is an alias for forElement(String, Obfuscator, CaseSensitivity) with the last specified default case sensitivity using XMLObfuscator.Builder.caseSensitiveByDefault() or XMLObfuscator.Builder.caseInsensitiveByDefault(). The default is CaseSensitivity.CASE_SENSITIVE.

        Parameters:
        element - The local name of the element.
        obfuscator - The obfuscator to use for obfuscating the attribute.
        Returns:
        An object that can be used to configure the attribute, or continue building XMLObfuscators.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - If the given element name or obfuscator is null.
        IllegalArgumentException - If an element with the same local name and the same case sensitivity was already added for the attribute.
        Since:
        1.3

        Sets the obfuscator to use for occurrences of the attribute for a specific element.

      • forElement

        XMLObfuscator.AttributeConfigurer forElement(QName element,
                                             Obfuscator obfuscator)
        Sets the obfuscator to use for occurrences of the attribute for a specific element. Any element added using this method will take precedence over elements added using forElement(String, Obfuscator) or forElement(String, Obfuscator, CaseSensitivity).
        Parameters:
        element - The qualified name of the element.
        obfuscator - The obfuscator to use for obfuscating the attribute.
        Returns:
        An object that can be used to configure the attribute, or continue building XMLObfuscators.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - If the given element name or obfuscator is null.
        IllegalArgumentException - If an element with the same qualified name was already added for the attribute.
        Since:
        1.3
